Here's a chart of the [card number:"K" suit:"D"/]'s position in the deck for each riffle iteration.
Notice how it it takes a long time to move the [card number:"K" suit:"D"/] up just a few positions, but once the [card number:"K" suit:"D"/] starts rising towards the top, it accelerates.

